source.name: NSF Freedom of Information Act Report for October 1, 2005 through September 30, 2006
source.description: This file contains the National Science Foundation's 2006 FOIA Annual Report. The report provides detailed information regarding the number and type of FOIA cases we processed in FY 2006. It also includes data regarding time and costs associated with processing these cases.
